{"article":"<section><h1 data-index=0>开发环境：添加 React 到现有应用</h1><p>也就是可控的定制化</p><section><h2 data-index=1>使用webpack：安装相关包</h2><pre><code>yarn add react react-dom babel-preset-react\n</code></pre></section></section><section><h1 data-index=2>状态</h1><section><h2 data-index=3>构造函数是唯一能够初始化 this.state 的地方</h2></section><section><h2 data-index=4>更新</h2><pre><code class=lang-js><span class=hljs-selector-tag>this</span><span class=hljs-selector-class>.setState</span>({<span class=hljs-attribute>comment</span>: <span class=hljs-string>'Hello'</span>});\n</code></pre></section><section><h2 data-index=5>使用</h2><pre><code class=lang-html><span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>h2</span>&gt;</span>It is {this.state.date.toLocaleTimeString()}.<span class=hljs-tag>&lt;/<span class=hljs-name>h2</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></section><section><h2 data-index=6>完整示例</h2><pre><code class=lang-js><span class=hljs-class><span class=hljs-keyword>class</span> <span class=hljs-title>Clock</span> <span class=hljs-keyword>extends</span> <span class=hljs-title>React</span>.<span class=hljs-title>Component</span> </span>{\n  <span class=hljs-keyword>constructor</span>(props) {\n    <span class=hljs-keyword>super</span>(props);\n    <span class=hljs-keyword>this</span>.state = {<span class=hljs-attr>date</span>: <span class=hljs-keyword>new</span> <span class=hljs-built_in>Date</span>()};\n  }\n\n  componentDidMount() {\n    <span class=hljs-keyword>this</span>.timerID = setInterval(\n      <span class=hljs-function><span class=hljs-params>()</span> =&gt;</span> <span class=hljs-keyword>this</span>.tick(),\n      <span class=hljs-number>1000</span>\n    );\n  }\n\n  render() {\n    <span class=hljs-keyword>return</span> (\n      <span class=xml><span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>div</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello, world!<span class=hljs-tag>&lt;/<span class=hljs-name>h1</span>&gt;</span>\n        <span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>h2</span>&gt;</span>It is {this.state.date.toLocaleTimeString()}.<span class=hljs-tag>&lt;/<span class=hljs-name>h2</span>&gt;</span>\n      <span class=hljs-tag>&lt;/<span class=hljs-name>div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n    );\n  }\n}\n</code></pre></section></section>","menu":"<div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"0\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">开发环境：添加 React 到现有应用</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"1\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">使用webpack：安装相关包</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"2\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">状态</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"3\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">构造函数是唯一能够初始化 this.state 的地方</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"4\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">更新</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"5\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">使用</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"6\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">完整示例</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div>"}